ALSA: hdspm - Use snd_ctl_enum_info() in snd_hdspm_info_autosync_ref

Also use snd_ctl_enum_info() to fill the autosync text fields on AES32
and MADI cards (only users of snd_hdspm_info_autosync_ref).

